            "heading": "Why drink Ingredients?",
            "heading_size": "medium",
            "heading_tag": "h4",
            "icon": "headset",
            "no_padding": true,
            "image": "",
            "content": "<p>Our ingredients are USDA certified organic, sourced directly from trusted farms worldwide, and rigorously lab-tested for purity. Every product is free from synthetic additives, artificial colors, and preservatives — delivering clean, functional ingredients you can trust for your most important creations.</p>",
