            "text": "<h3>Wholesale Available</h3><p>Looking to stock drink Ingredients for your business? We offer competitive bulk pricing, dedicated account support, and consistent quality for cafés, restaurants, wellness brands, and food manufacturers. Contact us for custom wholesale quotes.</p>",
