            "heading": "Product description",
            "image": "",
            "tab_image_width": 1000,
            "hide_image": false,
            "row_content": "<p>Every drink Ingredients product is USDA certified organic, sourced directly from trusted farms, and rigorously lab-tested for purity. No synthetic additives, no fillers — just clean, authentic ingredients.</p>",
